{"title_page": "Reem Shaikh", "text_new": "{{short description|Indian television actress}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=November 2019}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name               = Reem Shaikh\n| image              = Reem.Shaikh.jpg\n| caption            = Shaikh in 2019\n| birth_name         = Reem Sameer Shaikh<ref name=\"Facts\"/>\n| birth_date         = \n| birth_place        = [[Mumbai]], [[Maharashtra]], India<ref name=\"Facts\"/>\n| nationality        = Indian\n| occupation         = Actress\n| years_active       = 2010\u2014present\n}}\n'''Reem Sameer Shaikh''' is an Indian television actress.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/hindi/from-siddharth-nigam-jannat-zubair-rehmani-to-avneet-kaur-young-brigade-take-over-tv/photostory/66639384.cms|title=From Siddharth Nigam, Jannat Zubair Rehmani to Avneet Kaur: Young brigade take over TV|date=15 November 2018}}</ref> She is playing the role of Kalyani Malhar Rane in ''[[Tujhse Hai Raabta]]'' on [[Zee TV]] since September 2018.\n\n==Career==\nShaikh started her career as a child actor at the age of 6 with [[Neer Bhare Tere Naina Devi|''Neer Bhare Tere Naina Devi'']].<ref>{{cite news |title=Tujhse Hai Raabta's Reem Shaikh has grown from a young child actress into a gorgeous diva; see pics |url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/hindi/tujhse-hai-raabtas-reem-shaikh-has-grown-from-a-young-child-actress-into-a-gorgeous-diva-see-pics/photostory/68204247.cms |accessdate=7 February 2020 |work=The Times of India |date=28 February 2019 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Neer Bhare Tere Naina Devi child actress Reem Shaikh has evolved into a bombshell. See these pics to believe {{!}} Entertainment News |url=https://www.timesnownews.com/entertainment/news/people/photo-gallery/neer-bhare-tere-naina-devi-child-actress-reem-shaikh-has-evolved-into-a-bombshell-see-these-pics-to-believe/374847 |accessdate=7 February 2020 |work=www.timesnownews.com |date=6 March 2019 |language=en}}</ref>\n\nIn 2017, she landed a lead role in a film called \"Gul Makai\".<ref>{{cite web|url=https://m.hindustantimes.com/bollywood/reem-shaikh-plays-nobel-prize-winner-malala-yousufzai-in-her-biopic-gul-makai-watch-teaser/story-6zNosBUhttgiTExYGiHTAL.html|title=Shaikh plays Nobel Prize winner Malala Yousufzai in her biopic Gul Makai. Watch teaser|work=[[Hindustan Times]]|date=12 July 2018}}</ref>\n\nIn 2018, she guest-starred as Sanaya Seth on [[Colors TV]] popular show [[Tu Aashiqui]]. In the same year she booked the lead role of as Kalyani Malhar Rane in [[Zee TV]]'s new show [[Tujhse Hai Raabta]].<ref name=\"Facts\">{{cite web|url=http://www.tellychakkar.com/tv/tv-news/unknown-facts-about-tujhse-hai-raabta-lead-reem-shaikh-180923|title=UNKNOWN facts about Tujhse Hai Raabta lead Reem Shaikh|work=Telly Chakkar|date=23 September 2018}}</ref>\n\nIn 2019, she debuted in her first music video \"Aaja Sohniye\" released by [[Zee Music Company]]. The song is composed by Vaibhav Saxena.<ref>{{cite web |title=Aaja Sohniye - Official Music Video  {{!}} Reem Shaikh {{!}} Kshitij Vedi {{!}} Vaibhav Saxena |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g92U0FZSSHo |website=YouTube |publisher=Zee Music Company |accessdate=11 April 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=latest punjabi song 'Aaja Sohniye' sung by Kshitij Vedi |url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/videos/entertainment/music/punjabi/punjabi-song-2020-latest-punjabi-song-aaja-sohniye-sung-by-kshitij-vedi/videoshow/74730283.cms |work=ET Times |location=mumbai |date=20 March 2020 |access-date=20 March 2020 }}</ref>\n\n==Filmography==\n=== Television ===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! Notes\n|-\n| 2010\n|''[[Neer Bhare Tere Naina Devi]]''\n| Lakshmi/Devi\n| \n|-\n| 2011\n|''[[Na Aana Is Des Laado]]''\n| Mausam\n| Cameo\n|- \n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2012\n|''[[Me Aajji Aur Sahib]]''\n| Megha\n| \n|-\n|''[[The Suite Life of Karan & Kabir]]''\n| Shipra\n| Guest Appearance\n|-\n